{"tid":604824,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實90後都唔係咁差姐","createTime":"2018-03-25T06:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T13:33:55.000Z","uid":152001,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"774f02ee3f5d79d179951a671ba36b13a1183334","tid":604824,"uid":152001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"見到依張圖 以為90後果格係講緊00後<br />\n 諗番起今朝係名校secret睇到既00後<br />\n相比之下都唔係咁差姐 <br />\n雖然身邊都係有啲蝗用大陸apps<br />\n但普通話真係無乜聽見人係學校入面講<br />\n我唔排除10年後啲學生大部份都係講普通話<br />\n但起碼我依加同將來會講既只會係廣東話<br />\n寫既係正體字 <br />\n起碼我地都認為自己仲係香港人<br />\n唔係想搞分化 <br />\n只係覺得啲蝗落到黎香港<br />\n點解唔係適應我地既生活而係同化我地 <br />\n見到依加名校secret ig個post<br />\n真係覺得佢地個腦係咪生蟲<br />\n同化左既香港 咁同佢同係中國生活有咩分別<br />\nBetween以前唔會覺得全部00都係蝗 但見到ig post真心灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/141255_5f52dea5dab2d0f7e2fbff0f18f0f3a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F141255_5f52dea5dab2d0f7e2fbff0f18f0f3a5.png&h=953a2043&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b755238ca84cd3efeda3a59cbc83897230ea4c14","tid":604824,"uid":152001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"Btw見到fb到起碼都會多啲人留言屌番個樓主都叫開心番啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5824e01fdb335ed226010fe6a941da8d6ee8e39","tid":604824,"uid":152001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15641723f60aa2583bb6bca07929aeef4ae4c0f6","tid":604824,"uid":25916,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:22:10.000Z","msg":"話90後唔識金庸已經錯晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4331e9b2a599449c89fb1aa5ef322d4b6931c0","tid":604824,"uid":118322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:25:07.000Z","ms